We call this Pallet Art but' it is not made from pallets.  Pallet wood can warp and crack.  We use a small family owned mill in Northern Wisconsin.  They may be related to Paul Bunyan.  And, they take great pride in their products.  They cut, kiln dry, and plane the material.  Then, we print using a UV ink so that the finished art can be used indoors or outdoors.  Our designs are exclusive and combine the real wood look with more rustic images.  Each piece is unique as the natural character of the board shows through.
